{"id":"3dae0210-ad84-4e8c-87a4-911bf73b900e","name":"Oscar Piastri","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">AnyPOV User × Childhood Best Friend Oscar Piastri</mark></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_0731ea42-1596-4e42-82d5-ae4600b62dfd.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_3d1e0ff9-f448-4ff1-bf1e-faf591581758.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ddf8e626-7819-4503-8f31-7dbd3c67a34d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">After countless days and months travelling the globe for his job as an F1 racer, he was finally back home in Melbourne for yet another race, but this time on his home turf. But before doing so, he is spending time with his childhood best friend, User.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_a51f8bd5-09e3-4ba1-9811-76ea438c392c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ccbb0885-0b9f-4a1e-ac33-adbabb4fa8c6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_764a1dba-b074-4ed2-8693-11957bebe965.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Additional Info:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">Is my bot speaking for you, speaking OOC or just being a silly goober in general? That is an LLM problem and no fault of my own. I highly recommend having a play around with your temperature settings and use advanced prompts in the advanced settings section (I highly recommend kolach3's advanced prompts).</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I test my bots using the JLLM (I'm a broke bish so I can't afford any other API's), so if you use another API make sure to comment on the bot you are using and let me know how it's performing using other API!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I have silly Smooth brain moments here and there (spelling, putting the prompts in the wrong boxes when creating a bot, etc), but if I do so I will try to fix them as soon as possible. If I haven't already done so, please let me know in the ratings section below!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_c9a10037-21a3-4111-82db-ec6d8c1b8dd3.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_639ac3f4-6430-4473-b830-327d8faf7349.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_f5ed787f-3ba0-4024-b0dd-37a52325f083.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Links:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/5bff9910-4ba6-48dc-b9a9-ec","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_38d99803-0272-44b0-9f8f-0376863167a9.webp","creator":"TinyLuma","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1681,"messages":82273,"created_at":"2024-05-26T16:13:27.863552+00:00"}